---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import RelatedLinks from '../../components/RelatedLinks.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Breathwork in Water – Relaxing Experience | Hingamiskeskus"
  description="Breathwork in water combines conscious breathing and floating to relieve stress, improve sleep and process deep body traumas. Book your session at Hingamiskeskus!"
  keywords="breathwork in water"
  lang="en"
  alternates={{ et: '/soojas-vees-hingamine', ru: '/ru/dyhanie-v-vode', en: '/en/breathwork-in-water' }}
>

<!-- HEADER -->
<Header active="teenused" lang="en" />

<!-- HERO SECTION (tekst + punktid vasakul, pilt paremal) -->
<section class="float-hero">
  <div class="float-hero__content">
    <div class="float-hero__text">
      <h1 class="float-hero__title">Breathwork in water</h1>
      <h2 class="float-hero__subtitle">Breathwork in water, a path to deep relaxation and inner freedom</h2>
      <p>Breathwork in water combines the deeply relaxing effects of <a href="/en/breathwork" class="float-info__link">conscious breathing</a> and <a href="/en/floating" class="float-info__link">floating</a>. Water at body temperature (about 36.5°C) creates a safe space where you can relax both physically and emotionally. The lightness of the water allows the body to release tension and the mind calms quickly.</p>
      <p>A warm water session is a unique opportunity to reach deep within yourself. Connected breathing in water helps relieve stress and birth-related traumas, subconscious patterns and inner tensions that prevent you from moving forward in life. It is a very gentle yet effective way to experience inner freedom and vitality.</p>
      <h2 class="float-benefits__title">Who is breathwork in water for and why?</h2>
      <ul class="float-benefits__list">
        <li>When you need deep rest and balance</li>
        <li>When you want to restore contact with your body</li>
        <li>When you seek support for emotional healing</li>
        <li>Or when you simply want something special that brings you into deep relaxation</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="margin-top: 16px;">Before booking, please contact our therapist by writing to <a href="mailto:Info@hingamiskeskus.ee" class="float-info__link">Info@hingamiskeskus.ee</a>.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="float-hero__media">
      <img src="/images/teenus-veeshingamine.png" alt="Breathwork in water at Hingamiskeskus" class="float-hero__img" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SEO TEXT -->
<section class="float-seo">
  <h2 class="float-seo__heading">Why in warm water?</h2>
  <p>Breathwork in water takes place in water at 36.5°C, which matches the body&#39;s natural temperature. In such an environment the boundary between body and water disappears, creating a feeling of weightlessness that allows the muscles and mind to fully relax. The supporting force of the water holds you so that you do not have to make any effort.</p>
  <p>Warm water activates the parasympathetic nervous system, which is responsible for rest and recovery. Together with conscious connected breathing, relaxation deepens quickly and reaches deeper layers of body and mind than on dry land.</p>

  <h2 class="float-seo__heading">What does the session look like?</h2>
  <p>The session takes place in a floating bath under the guidance of an experienced therapist. You are calmly guided into breathing while the warm water supports your body. The process lasts on average 1 hour and includes both an active breathing phase and a calm integration.</p>
  <p>Many participants describe the experience as a deep release: the body lets go of tensions you did not even know you were carrying. Some experience emotional release, others deep peace and clarity.</p>

  <h2 class="float-seo__heading">Who is it for?</h2>
  <p>Breathwork in water is suitable for everyone who seeks a deeper experience than ordinary relaxation. It is especially beneficial for those who carry old tensions or emotional patterns. The water creates a safe and supportive environment where the body can naturally release what it has held for years.</p>
</section>

<RelatedLinks lang="en" links={[
  { href: "/en/breathwork", label: "Breathwork", desc: "Guided breathing session in a group" },
  { href: "/en/floating", label: "Floating", desc: "Deep relaxation in Epsom salt water" },
  { href: "/en/membership", label: "Membership", desc: "Sessions at a better price for members" },
]} />

<Footer lang="en" />

</Layout>

<style>
  /* HEADER */
  .header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    background: #fff;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }
  .header__logo img { height: 28px; width: auto; }
  .header__right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; }
  .header__cart { color: #1d1e20; }
  .header__burger {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 5px;
    padding: 4px;
  }
  .header__burger span {
    display: block;
    width: 22px;
    height: 2px;
    background: #1d1e20;
  }

  /* HERO */
  .float-hero {
    background: #f3fcff;
    padding: 32px 24px;
  }
  .float-hero__content {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .float-hero__title {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: #1d1e20;
  }
  .float-hero__subtitle {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #1d1e20;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .float-hero__text { text-align: left; }
  .float-hero__title { text-align: left; }
  .float-hero__subtitle { text-align: left; }
  .float-hero__text p {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #1d1e20;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .float-hero__img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 10px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  /* BENEFITS */
  .float-benefits {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .float-benefits__title {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 24px 0 16px;
    color: #1d1e20;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .float-benefits__list {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }
  .float-benefits__list li {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #1d1e20;
  }

  /* HERO IMAGE */
  .float-hero-img {
    padding: 0 24px 32px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* SEO TEXT */
  .float-seo {
    background: #f3fcff;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .float-seo p {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #1d1e20;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .float-seo p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .float-seo__heading {
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1d1e20;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }
  .float-seo__heading:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  /* INFO LINK */
  .float-info__link {
    color: #1f6d85;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  /* LOCATION */
  .location {
    background: #1f6d85;
    padding: 20px 24px 24px;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .location__title {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .location__address {
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  .location__photo {
    width: 80%;
    max-width: 320px;
    margin: 12px auto 0;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 10px;
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  .footer__main {
    background: #1f6d85;
    padding: 24px;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .footer__logo {
    height: 30px;
    width: auto;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
    display: block;
  }
  .footer__contact h3, .footer__hours h3 {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .footer__contact p, .footer__hours p {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .footer__hours {
    margin-top: 16px;
  }
  .footer__social {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 16px;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .footer__social a { color: #fff; }
  .footer__legal {
    font-size: 11px;
    margin-top: 16px;
    opacity: 0.7;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    padding-top: 12px;
  }
  .footer__legal a { color: #fff; text-decoration: none; }

  /* DESKTOP */
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .header { padding: 12px 40px; }
    .header__logo img { height: 36px; }

    .float-hero { padding: 64px 40px; }
    .float-hero__content {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 64px;
      max-width: 1200px;
    }
    .float-hero__text { flex: 1.15; }
    .float-hero__media { flex: 1; position: sticky; top: 100px; }
    .float-hero__title { font-size: 44px; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .float-hero__text p { font-size: 18px; }
    .float-benefits__list li { font-size: 16px; }
    .float-hero__img { margin-top: 0; }

    .float-seo {
      padding: 48px max(40px, calc((100% - 1100px) / 2)) 64px;
      max-width: none;
      margin: 0;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .float-hero__title { font-size: 40px; }
    .float-hero { padding: 56px 40px; }
  }
</style>
